          </span>
          <span class="text-slate-700">&middot;</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-emerald-400/70">Updated March 11, 2026</span>
          <span class="text-slate-700">&middot;</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-600">Pedro</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-slate-100 leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6">
          We Scored Ourselves First &mdash; Here&apos;s What We Found
